ianchart\">{{cite web|url=https://www.parmuziku.lv/zinas/latvija/muzikas-paterina-tops-45-nedela-8218|title=M\u016bzikas Pat\u0113ri\u0146a Tops/ 45. ned\u0113\u013ca|language=Latvian|publisher=[[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry|LAIPA]]|accessdate=25 November 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108140426/https://www.parmuziku.lv/zinas/latvija/muzikas-paterina-tops-45-nedela-8218|archivedate=8 November 2019}}</ref>\n| 5\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Lebanon ([[The Official Lebanese Top 20|OLT20]])<ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web|url=http://www.olt20.com/Dua_Lipa#fragment-2&panel1-2|title=The Official Lebanese Top 20|publisher=[[The Official Lebanese Top 20]]|accessdate=25 January 2020}}</ref>\n| 7\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Lithuania ([[AGATA (organization)|AGATA]])<ref name=\"lithuanianchart\">{{cite web|url=https://www.agata.lt/lt/naujienos/savaites-klausomiausi-w45/|title=2019 45-os savait\u0117s klausomiausi (TOP 100)|language=Lithuanian|publisher=[[AGATA (organization)|AGATA]]|date=11 November 2019|accessdate=29 November 2019}}</ref>\n| 2\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Luxembourg Digital Songs (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref name=\"luxdigitalchart\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/luxembourg-digital-song-sales/2019-11-16|title=Luxembourg Digital Song Sales \u2013 November 16, 2019|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=19 November 2019}}</ref>\n| 4\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Malaysia ([[Recording Industry Association of Malaysia|RIM]])<ref name=\"malaysianchart\">{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/RecordingIndustryMalaysia/photos/pcb.3019967364697280/3019949714699045/?type=3&theater|title=Top 20 Most Streamed International & Domestic Singles In Malaysia|language=English|work=[[Recording Industry Association of Malaysia]]|publisher=Recording Industry Association of Malaysia|accessdate=18 November 2019}}</ref>\n| 7\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Mexico Airplay]] (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref name=\"mexicana